column2: ALPHA BLACK TO PAPA BEAR. WE HAVE CLEARED OUT THE INTERSECTION. OVER.
ALPHA TO PAPA BEAR. CHOKE POINT IS CLEARED. SEND IN THE TANKS. OVER.
ALPHA TO PAPA BEAR. WE HAVE NEUTRALIZED ENEMY ARMOR THREAT. OVER.
PAPA BEAR TO ALPHA BLACK. COPY. PROCEED. OVER.
PAPA BEAR TO ALPHA. ROGER THAT. SENDING THE TANKS. OVER.
PAPA BEAR TO ALPHA. HEADS UP WE HAVE ENEMY ARMOR MOVEMENT IN THE WEST. GET READY TO REPEL ANY ATTACKS. OVER.
